snippet.title: Season 13: Spellbinder Official Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
Transform into the ultimate master of witchcraft with the Mythic Spellbinder Widowmaker skin. Go from potions apprentice to master of witchcraft by unlocking all four levels with the Mythic Prisms earned in the Premium Battle Pass.

Get ready for spine-chilling action in a haunting new Halloween Terror game mode, Junkenstein’s Laboratory–a fast-paced Team Deathmatch where you can enhance your heroes with powerful cursed talent cards.

Good and evil will collide in our newest collaboration, Overwatch 2 x My Hero Academia.

Enjoy new Map updates, Shop Bundles, spooky surprises, and SO much more.

Have a ghoulishly good time when Overwatch 2 Season 13: Spellbinder arrives Oct 15.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!

© K. Horikoshi / Shueisha, My Hero Academia Project
